From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: WebKitGTKWin Port <webkitgtkwin@local>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] WebKitGTKWin: keep libintl printf macros out of PrintStream

MinGW libintl.h redirects printf/vprintf with preprocessor macros. When a
translation unit includes GLib gettext helpers before WTF print headers, those
macros rewrite C++ member names such as PrintStream::printf and
StringPrintStream::vprintf. Undefine them before declaring the WTF print API.
---
 Source/WTF/wtf/PrintStream.h | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/Source/WTF/wtf/PrintStream.h b/Source/WTF/wtf/PrintStream.h
index 59da841f5f36..5f8bdf14bc17 100644
--- a/Source/WTF/wtf/PrintStream.h
+++ b/Source/WTF/wtf/PrintStream.h
@@ -39,6 +39,11 @@
 #include <wtf/RefPtr.h>
 #include <wtf/StdLibExtras.h>
 
+#if defined(__MINGW32__)
+#undef printf
+#undef vprintf
+#endif
+
 namespace WTF {
 
 inline const char* boolForPrinting(bool value)
-- 
2.43.0
